description: RentIT is a streamlined rental platform that has been redesigned using HTML, CSS, and Bootstrap to enhance user experience and visual appeal. The updated interface features a responsive design for optimal use across all devices, modern aesthetics with improved accessibility, and user-friendly forms for easier property listings and rental inquiries. With advanced search functionality and dynamic real-time updates, RentIT efficiently connects property owners with renters, offering a contemporary and rental process.
Development of a new mobile application for e-commerce platform.
